Analiza nestacionarnosti govornih signalov¶

Uporabili bomo različne dolžine oken in stopnje prekrivanja.

import numpy as np
import scipy.io.wavfile as wavfile
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import os

soundFolder = './sound'
windowLengthsMs = [10, 20, 50, 100]
overlapRatios = [0.0, 0.5, 0.75]
useHammingOptions = [False, True]

Utils¶

In [2]:
def readWavFile(filePath):
    sampleRate, data = wavfile.read(filePath)
    if len(data.shape) > 1:
        data = data[:, 0]
    return sampleRate, data

def plotSpectrogram(stftMatrix, timeAxis, freqAxis, title, ax):
    pcm = ax.pcolormesh(timeAxis, freqAxis, stftMatrix, shading='auto')
    ax.set_title(title, fontsize=8)
    ax.set_ylabel('Frekvenca (Hz)')
    ax.set_xlabel('Čas (s)')
    return pcm

Funkcije za analizu¶

Shorter windows (e.g., 10 ms) capture rapid changes in speech, suitable for fast speaking rates. Longer windows (e.g., 100 ms) smooth out variations, better for slower speech. Overlap (50% or 75%) improves time resolution.

In [3]:
def applyHammingWindow(signal, windowLength):
    window = np.hamming(windowLength)
    return signal * window

def computeStft(signal, sampleRate, windowLengthMs, overlapRatio, useHamming):
    windowLength = int(windowLengthMs * sampleRate / 1000)
    stepSize = int(windowLength * (1 - overlapRatio))
    if stepSize == 0:
        stepSize = 1
    nFrames = int(np.ceil((len(signal) - windowLength) / stepSize)) + 1
    paddedLength = windowLength + (nFrames - 1) * stepSize
    paddedSignal = np.pad(signal, (0, paddedLength - len(signal)), 'constant')
    maxFreq = 3000
    freqLimit = int(maxFreq * windowLength / sampleRate) + 1
    stftMatrix = []
    for i in range(0, paddedLength - windowLength + 1, stepSize):
        frame = paddedSignal[i:i + windowLength]
        if useHamming:
            frame = applyHammingWindow(frame, windowLength)
        spectrum = np.fft.fft(frame)
        spectrum = np.abs(spectrum[:freqLimit])
        stftMatrix.append(spectrum)
    stftMatrix = np.array(stftMatrix).T
    timeAxis = np.arange(nFrames) * stepSize / sampleRate
    freqAxis = np.arange(freqLimit) * sampleRate / windowLength
    return stftMatrix, timeAxis, freqAxis

Obdelava signalov¶

Za vsak signal v mapi izračunamo STFT z različnimi dolžinami oken in prekrivanji.

In [4]:
for fileName in os.listdir(soundFolder):
    if fileName.endswith('.wav'):
        sampleRate, signal = readWavFile(os.path.join(soundFolder, fileName))
        fig, axes = plt.subplots(4, 6, figsize=(20, 12))
        fig.suptitle(f'Spektrogrami za {fileName}', fontsize=16)
        for i, windowLengthMs in enumerate(windowLengthsMs):
            for j, overlapRatio in enumerate(overlapRatios):
                for k, useHamming in enumerate(useHammingOptions):
                    stftMatrix, timeAxis, freqAxis = computeStft(signal, sampleRate, windowLengthMs, overlapRatio, useHamming)
                    title = f'Okno: {windowLengthMs}ms, Prekrivanje: {int(overlapRatio*100)}%, Hamming: {useHamming}'
                    ax = axes[i, j * 2 + k]
                    pcm = plotSpectrogram(stftMatrix, timeAxis, freqAxis, title, ax)
        cbarAx = fig.add_axes([0.65, 0.98, 0.25, 0.02])
        fig.colorbar(pcm, cax=cbarAx, label='Amplituda (dB)', orientation='horizontal')
        plt.tight_layout(rect=[0, 0, 1, 0.95])
        plt.show()
        plt.close()

Vprašanje 1: Nestacionarnost in hitrost izgovarjave¶

Preučimo, kako hitrost izgovarjave vpliva na nestacionarnost. Hitrejša izgovarjava ima hitrejše spremembe v frekvenčni vsebini, zato potrebujemo krajša okna za boljše sledenje. Primerjamo spektrograme dveh signalov z različno hitrostjo izgovarjave.

In [5]:
fastFile = './sounds/erozijaFast.wav'
slowFile = './sounds/erozijaSlow.wav'
sampleRateFast, fastSignal = readWavFile(fastFile)
sampleRateSlow, slowSignal = readWavFile(slowFile)
windowLengthMs = 20
overlapRatio = 0.5
useHamming = True
stftFast, timeAxisFast, freqAxisFast = computeStft(fastSignal, sampleRateFast, windowLengthMs, overlapRatio, useHamming)
stftSlow, timeAxisSlow, freqAxisSlow = computeStft(slowSignal, sampleRateSlow, windowLengthMs, overlapRatio, useHamming)
fig, (ax1, ax2) = plt.subplots(1, 2, figsize=(12, 4))
pcm1 = plotSpectrogram(stftFast, timeAxisFast, freqAxisFast, 'Hitra izgovarjava, 20ms, 50% prekrivanje', ax1)
plotSpectrogram(stftSlow, timeAxisSlow, freqAxisSlow, 'Počasna izgovarjava, 20ms, 50% prekrivanje', ax2)
cbarAx = fig.add_axes([0.40, 0.94, 0.25, 0.03])
fig.colorbar(pcm1, cax=cbarAx, label='Amplituda (dB)', orientation='horizontal')
plt.tight_layout(rect=[0, 0, 1, 0.9])
plt.subplots_adjust(wspace=0.3)
plt.show()
plt.close()

Vprašanje 2: Višji harmoniki¶

Z daljšimi okni dobimo boljšo frekvenčno ločljivost, kar omogoča boljšo zaznavo višjih harmonikov. Primerjamo spektrograme z okni 10 ms in 100 ms za en signal.

In [6]:
sampleFile = './sounds/OHigh.wav'
sampleRate, signal = readWavFile(sampleFile)
windowLengthsMs = [10, 100]
overlapRatio = 0.5
useHamming = True
fig, axes = plt.subplots(1, 2, figsize=(12, 4))
for i, windowLengthMs in enumerate(windowLengthsMs):
    stftMatrix, timeAxis, freqAxis = computeStft(signal, sampleRate, windowLengthMs, overlapRatio, useHamming)
    title = f'Višji harmoniki, Okno: {windowLengthMs}ms, 50% prekrivanje'
    pcm = plotSpectrogram(stftMatrix, timeAxis, freqAxis, title, axes[i])
cbarAx = fig.add_axes([0.40, 0.0, 0.25, 0.03])
fig.colorbar(pcm, cax=cbarAx, label='Amplituda (dB)', orientation='horizontal')
plt.tight_layout()
plt.show()
plt.close()

Vprašanje 3: Razlikovanje samoglasnikov¶

Krajša okna omogočajo boljšo časovno ločljivost, kar je ključno za razlikovanje samoglasnikov, saj imajo različne frekvenčne vzorce. Primerjamo spektrograme za samoglasnika 'a' in 'o' z oknom 100 ms.

In [7]:
vowelAFile = './sounds/ALow.wav'
vowelOFile = './sounds/OLow.wav'
sampleRateA, signalA = readWavFile(vowelAFile)
sampleRate0, signalO = readWavFile(vowelOFile)
windowLengthMs = 100
overlapRatio = 0.5
useHamming = True
fig, (ax1, ax2) = plt.subplots(1, 2, figsize=(12, 4))
stftA, timeAxisA, freqAxisA = computeStft(signalA, sampleRateA, windowLengthMs, overlapRatio, useHamming)
stftO, timeAxisO, freqAxisO = computeStft(signalO, sampleRate0, windowLengthMs, overlapRatio, useHamming)
plotSpectrogram(stftA, timeAxisA, freqAxisA, 'Samoglasnik A, 20ms, 50% prekrivanje', ax1)
plotSpectrogram(stftO, timeAxisO, freqAxisO, 'Samoglasnik O, 20ms, 50% prekrivanje', ax2)
cbarAx = fig.add_axes([0.4, 0.0, 0.25, 0.03])
fig.colorbar(pcm1, cax=cbarAx, label='Amplituda (dB)', orientation='horizontal')
plt.tight_layout()
plt.show()
plt.close()
